dialog_add(noone, "[#E24A33]It gave me one final chance to see you again.[/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]You have deceived yourself in your blind devotion.[/c]");
dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]You know that we could never be together, Qiu Ye.[/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#E24A33]All our memories, did they mean nothing to you?[/c]");
dialog_add(noone, "[#E24A33]Our hopes… Our dreams… Your legacy?[/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]You understand nothing.[/c]"); //11
dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]This is why I could never reveal the truth to you.[/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#E24A33]What are you saying?[/c]");
dialog_add(noone, "[#E24A33]I died for you, was that not enough?[/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]I killed myself to seal the dragon with me for eternity.[/c]");
dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]But you have revived me for your selfish desires![/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#E24A33]No... What have I done?[/c]");

dialog_add(noone, "[#333FC2]If I am not put to rest again, \nthe dragon will use my body as its vessel to destroy the world.[/c]");

